5:
Trust in Yahweh with all your heart
\q and do not lean on your own understanding;
\q

7:
Do not be wise in your own eyes;
\q fear Yahweh and turn away from evil.
\q

13:
The one who finds wisdom is blessed;
\q he also gets understanding.
\q

23:
Then you will walk on your way in safety
\q and your foot will not stumble;
\q
